HEADWORD: Inviolableness
<hw>In*vi"o*la*ble*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of
being inviolable; <as>as, the <ex>inviolableness</ex> of divine
justice</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

